data.description: Introducing 1627 N Long Ave - a charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the heart of Chicago's lovely North Austin neighborhood.    Step inside to find a spacious layout with a bright and open front room smoothly flowing into the formal dining room, providing tons of space and flexibility for entertaining. Soak up the sun in your generous backyard - perfect for gardening, playtime, and relaxation.    Upstairs, enjoy bedrooms and a full bath bathroom, as well as a spacious kitchen.  There is also an attic for tons of storage, or potentially a future addition - builders take note.  Downstairs features a separate access to two bedrooms and a full bathroom, as well as an long bar for hosting friends. Conveniently situated near North Avenue, residents will love quick access to an array of shops, restaurants, and entertainment. You are just five minutes away your favorite Starbucks at the Washington Square Mall.  They also have a full gym there, as well as various shopping options, and a modern gym.  Whether you're a growing family, ready to downsize, or simply investing in the dynamic North Austin real estate market - 1627 N Long offers incredible value and amenities wrapped up in charming fashion. Don't miss your chance to make this fabulous house your new home.  We look forward to working with you.
